headline: Labcorp Announces Collaboration with Roche to Advance Digital Pathology Capabilities
summary: Labcorp (NYSE: LH), a global leader of innovative and comprehensive laboratory services, announced today a collaboration with Roche to implement the company's FDA-cleared VENTANA® DP 600 and DP 200 slide scanners. The investment enables pathologists to diagnose patients using digital images and supports future artificial intelligence (AI) integration.
